William,<br><br>
They didn't walk north because they were  the insurrection in the south. They were named the Viet Cong.<br><br>
I think your service and mine is justified, as you say, because we answered the call. If I was not proud of my service, I wouldn't be posting on this site.<br><br>
However, to *avoid or refuse* to take part in what you term, &quot;the stupid things done over there, the stupid people in charge, and insane policies&quot; is something that I am able to &quot;repect&quot;.<br><br>
Like you, I served. But, I am unable to pass judgment on those who did not serve because I saw all of those things you refer to, and would not wish for anyone to undergo them.<br><br>
Welcome Home William, and I hope that you will take part in these discussions.
